  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4374230/extras/5bc7871ac1a784162f75dc8116b08adf.avif?t=1773704985\" width=1200 height=401 /></span><strong><i>Maestro is a student Fast Paced First person Roguelite set in a mysterious casino where you will fight your way to the top by shooting cards, using abilities, upgrade your card with gambling and creating builds to your liking.</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4374230/extras/be560a1ac0c9aa86a947a23b85f98182.poster.avif?t=1773704985\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4374230/extras/be560a1ac0c9aa86a947a23b85f98182.webm?t=1773704985\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4374230/extras/be560a1ac0c9aa86a947a23b85f98182.mp4?t=1773704985\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4374230/extras/6df14a82475ae9aa3720609be2292498.avif?t=1773704985\" width=1560 height=197 /></span><i><strong>Explore the 3 Floor of the psychedelic and colourful Casino. In each floor, you will need to survive 6 rooms before acceding the shop and fight the boss. Each Floor has their own environment, enemies and boss.</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4374230/extras/6947a95fbea2621d8723e3c299556dfa.poster.avif?t=1773704985\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4374230/extras/6947a95fbea2621d8723e3c299556dfa.webm?t=1773704985\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4374230/extras/6947a95fbea2621d8723e3c299556dfa.mp4?t=1773704985\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4374230/extras/ff599cb8ca03f24e55177b231d38dbe9.avif?t=1773704985\" width=1560 height=158 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">At the end of each room, you will have the choice between two rooms that will give you either a card, an ability, an upgrade or money. Your will need to choose wisely to optimise your build to your need.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4374230/extras/53e57961540b60ca9861a4d83baba7ba.avif?t=1773704985\" width=1560 height=146 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">With multiple cards and abilities at your disposition, you will have the opportunity to create different build each run to suits your gameplay style.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4374230/extras/7838c04ed069bb7ce69caf68e0a7b321.avif?t=1773704985\" width=1560 height=146 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><i><strong>In each Shop Room, you will be able to play Blackjack to upgrade any card that you have.</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4374230/extras/84a7c322f2d2b735403cf60640daf975.poster.avif?t=1773704985\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4374230/extras/84a7c322f2d2b735403cf60640daf975.webm?t=1773704985\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4374230/extras/84a7c322f2d2b735403cf60640daf975.mp4?t=1773704985\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4374230/extras/7857067fc0619f85dc9801b6b014e2d1.avif?t=1773704985\" width=1560 height=146 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">By going in upgrade room or by destroying the golden slot machine, you will be able to pick up upgrade like damage upgrade, Max health Upgrade and more !</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4374230/extras/1f82c214f3b80f4d1c423171a6ccd7ab.poster.avif?t=1773704985\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4374230/extras/1f82c214f3b80f4d1c423171a6ccd7ab.webm?t=1773704985\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4374230/extras/1f82c214f3b80f4d1c423171a6ccd7ab.mp4?t=1773704985\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4374230/extras/5bc7871ac1a784162f75dc8116b08adf.avif?t=1773704985\" width=1200 height=401 /></span><strong><i>Maestro is a student Fast Paced First person Roguelite set in a mysterious casino where you will fight your way to the top by shooting cards, using abilities, upgrade your card with gambling and creating builds to your liking.</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4374230/extras/be560a1ac0c9aa86a947a23b85f98182.poster.avif?t=1773704985\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4374230/extras/be560a1ac0c9aa86a947a23b85f98182.webm?t=1773704985\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4374230/extras/be560a1ac0c9aa86a947a23b85f98182.mp4?t=1773704985\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4374230/extras/6df14a82475ae9aa3720609be2292498.avif?t=1773704985\" width=1560 height=197 /></span><i><strong>Explore the 3 Floor of the psychedelic and colourful Casino. In each floor, you will need to survive 6 rooms before acceding the shop and fight the boss. Each Floor has their own environment, enemies and boss.</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item