 you have.</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4374230/extras/84a7c322f2d2b735403cf60640daf975.poster.avif?t=1773704985\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4374230/extras/84a7c322f2d2b735403cf60640daf975.webm?t=1773704985\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4374230/extras/84a7c322f2d2b735403cf60640daf975.mp4?t=1773704985\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4374230/extras/7857067fc0619f85dc9801b6b014e2d1.avif?t=1773704985\" width=1560 height=146 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">By going in upgrade room or by destroying the golden slot machine, you will be able to pick up upgrade like damage upgrade, Max health Upgrade and more !</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4374230/extras/1f82c214f3b80f4d1c423171a6ccd7ab.poster.avif?t=1773704985\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4374230/extras/1f82c214f3b80f4d1c423171a6ccd7ab.webm?t=1773704985\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4374230/extras/1f82c214f3b80f4d1c423171a6ccd7ab.mp4?t=1773704985\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
