      "review_text": "So I boot up the game,pretty excited.\nFirst thing I notice? I check my FPS with Steam overlay and almost had a heart attack......GPU at 80% and CPU at 90%....\n\nI literally asked myself:   \"Am I playing a game or mining Bitcoin right now?\"\n\nMaybe it was just an aggressive boot-up,or maybe my PC was about to take off.\nWho knows.\n\nafter the panic attack,I actually played the tutorial.    And wow,the tutorial is decent.\nReally well done,teaches you everything,super clear!\n\nThen came the moment: choosing my first ability.\nAnd there it was... a BAZOOKA!!!\nLadies and gentlemen, I chose the bazooka. No hesitation. :))))))\n\nThe concept is really interesting,and you can see the potential.\nBut yeah, it needs some serious optimization.My PC shouldn't feel like it's running Crysis when I'm just starting a tutorial.\n\nsome NPCs has that samurai pose like they're waiting for a duel.\n\nJust please let my GPU breathe.\n\nAlso, if you're reading this, please check out my artwork!\nhttps://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=3668605748\n\nI would appreciate some upvotes, awards, comments, and adding it to favorites!",
      "timestamp_created": 1773715619
    },
